name: Tail
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.
The smart-contract owner can mint new tokens, please proceed with caution.

description.en: $TAIL is the predominant rewards token in the Sanin Inu ecosystem. Much like a dog is given a sense of balance and stability by its own tail, our $TAIL provides the backbone for our dream of a decentralized system. These tokens play a pivotal role in maintaining the balance of community and ecosystem alike, and is therefore crucial to our goals of decentralization.
